item.title: Server won't run?
item.dc:creator: @SpectralX SpectralX
item.description:
@SpectralX wrote:

[quote=“bibbobbib, post:3, topic:432201”]@echo off title SERVERNAME "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\java.exe" -Xmx1011m -cp bin;deps/poi.jar;deps/mysql.jar;deps/mina.jar;deps/slf4j.jar;deps/slf4j-nop.jar;deps/jython.jar;log4j-1.2.15.jar; server.Server pause

Try that. make sure you have the right JDK version "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\ here if you need help finding your JDK version comment or pm me[/quote]

OMG Thanks I’m good at coding I was just lost… LOL THANKS SO MUCH! I never knew I would ever have a problem with this.
